Invocation Name: beam me up
Developer Terms of Use
des: BeMup offers transportation on-demand as a replacement for your dedicated car. With a BeMup subscription, you obtain mileage that you can use to book trips 24/7. For each trip, the distance plus a fixed start amount (4-10 km) trip will be taken off the balance. You must have sufficient kilometers in your account for a trip you book. Subscriptions are for the shared use of our vehicles. At a premium, you can get exclusive use of a vehicle for all your trips. Please review actual service operation availability in your region on our website bemup.club. Subscriptions need to be started using our mobile apps for IOS or Android. The first month of service is free, subsequent months of usage are paid in advance.
